ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST in order to include carbon and speciality steel product on the Import Control List for a further three years beginning on October 31, 2017 which will provide the Canadian steel-producing industry with accurate and timely statistics on imports into Canada to facilitate early detection of the dumping of goods on the Canadian market, allowing early investigation by the Canada Border Services Agency and remedial action, if required.
